{"id":149987,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/英全民公投决定是否改变现行选举机制/","date":"2011-05-05T10:30:28Z","modified":"2011-05-05T10:30:28Z","title":"英全民公投决定是否改变现行选举机制","content":"<div>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">伦敦</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">英国本周四举行是否更改现行选举制的全民公决。</span><span>4600</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">万登记选民将在</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">“</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">排序复选制</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">”</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和现行的</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">“</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">简单多数制</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">”</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">之间做出选择。公投初步结果将于周五晚间公布。民意调查结果显示，多数英国人赞同保留简单多数机制。围绕是否修改现行选举制，联合执政的保守党和自民党产生严重分歧。保守党籍的卡梅伦首相要求保留简单多数制，自民党籍的副首相克莱格则将改革选举机制作为继续参政的先决条件。批评者指出，根据简单多数制产生的选举结果不能真实反映出某政党所获实际票数，而只是反映了所赢得的选区。如采用排序复选制，小党的机会将得到改善。</span></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C15050535%2C00.html%3Fmaca%3Dchi-rss-chi-all-1127-rdf&#038;title=%E8%8B%B1%E5%85%A8%E6%B0%91%E5%85%AC%E6%8A%95%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E6%94%B9%E5%8F%98%E7%8E%B0%E8%A1%8C%E9%80%89%E4%B8%BE%E6%9C%BA%E5%88%B6\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[11961]}